_sText:
Basic gg/fy map.  Has buyzones if you don't like gg.  Maximum server support is 32.  If you need more player slots, let me know and I will make some more.

10 is definitely the best amount of people to play with.  Too many people is just too crowded.

If you like the map and want more, tell me.  I also take some special map requests from clans.  If you are getting some weird error, tell me.  If you need anything else or want something tweaked then let me know, I will more than likely be able to change it.

Email: ace.asp@gmail.com

Come play on this special server that has hosted my map:

72.51.41.228:27015





A V2 will be made shortly with cell shading :D
